[{"Id": 1013645, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "This is the place of the Prophet Ibrahim’s house, from where he used to ready himself for fighting against the giants. At this place, you may offer a 2 rakat namaz. After the namaz recite Tasbeeh-e-Zahra (s) and then recite…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Yeh maqaam-e-Ibrahim (a) jo unka ghar hai. Yahan se woh Amaalqa (giants) se jang karne gaye thay. Is maqaam par 2 rakat namaz anjaam de. Namaz ke baad Tasbeeh-e-Zahra (s) aur phir is tarah padhe…", "UrduDescription": "اس کے بعد اس گوشے میں چلا جائے جو شمال ومغرب کی طرف ہے۔ حضرت ابراہیم ؑ کا گھر اسی گوشے میں تھا اور یہیں سے آپ عمالقہ سے جنگ کرنے گئے تھے اس مقام پر ۲ رکعت نماز بجالائے بعد میں تسبیح فاطمہؑ زہراء پڑھ کر پھر کہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlu