 null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013646, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, (I beseech You) in the name of this holy area and in the name of him who used to worship You here. You know my need; so, (please) send blessings upon Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad and settle them for me. You have accounted my sins; so, (please) send blessings upon Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad and forgive them for me. O Allah, (please do) keep me alive as long as life is better for me, cause me to die if death is better for me, cause me to die bearing loyalty to Your intimate servants and antagonism against Your enemies, and do to me that which befits You, O most merciful of all those who show mercy!", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Us sharaf o barkat waale makaan ke waaste se aur uske waaste se jo us mein Teri ibaadat karta hai, Tu meri haajato’n ko jaanta hai pas Muhammad (s.a.w.a) par rehmat kar aur meri haajaat puri farma, Tu mere gunaho’n ko jaanta hai pas Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par rehmat naazil farma aur mere gunah bakhsh de. Ay Ma’bood! Mujhe zindah rakh jab tak zindagi mere liye behtar hai aur mujhe maut de jab maut mere liye behtar ho, keh woh Tere dosto’n ki mohabbat par aur Tere dushmano se adaawat par ho aur mere saath woh sulook kar jo Tere laayaq hai, ay sab se ziyadah rahem karne waale.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! اس شرف وبرکت والے مکان کے واسطے سے اور اس کے واسطے سے جو اس میں تیری عبادت کرتا ہے تو میری حاجتوں کو جانتا ہےپس محمدؐ وآل محمدؑ پر رحمت کر اور میری حاجات پوری فرما تو میرے گناہوں کو جانتا ہے پس محمدؐ وآل محمدؑ پر رحمت نازل فرما اور میرے گناہ بخش دے اے معبود! مجھے زندہ رکھ جب تک زندگی میرے لئے بہتر ہے اور مجھے موت دے جب موت میرے لئے بہتر ہو کہ وہ تیرے دوستوں کی محبت پر اورتیرے دشمنوں سے عداوت پر ہو اور میرے ساتھ وہ سلوک کر جو تیرے لائق ہے اے سب سے زیادہ رحم کرنے والے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA BE-HAQQE HAAZEHIL BUQ-A’TISH SHAREEFATE WA BE-HAQQE MAN TA-A’BBADA LAKA FEEHAA QAD A’LIMTA HAWAAA-EJEE FA-SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIWN WA AALE MOHAMMADIWN WAQ-ZEHAA WA QAD AH-SAYTA ZONOOBEE FA-SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIWN WA AALE MOHAMMADIWN WAGH-FIRHAA ALLAAHUMMA AHYENEE MAA KAANATIL HAYAATO KHAYRAN LEE WA AMITNEE EZAA KAANATIL WAFAATO KHAYRAL LEE A’LAA MOWAALAATE AWLE-YAAA-EKA WA MO-A’ADAATE A-A’DAAA-EKA WAF-A’L BEE MAA ANTA AHLOHU YAA ARHAMAR RAAHEMEEN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰھُمَّ بِحَقِّ ھٰذِهِ الْبُقْعَۃِ الشَّرِیْفَۃِ وَبِحَقِّ مَنْ تَعَبَّدَ لَكَ فِیْھَا قَدْ عَلِمْتَ حَوَآئِجِیْ فَصَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاقْضِھَا وَقَدْ اَحْصَیْتَ ذُنُوْبِیْ فَصَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاغْفِرْھَا۔ اَللّٰھُمَّ اَحْیِنِیْ مَا كَانَتِ الْحَیٰوۃُ خَیْرًا لِیْ وَاَمِتْنِیْ اِذَا كَانَتِ الْوَفَاۃُ خَیْرًا لِّیْ عَلٰی مُوَالَاۃِ اَوْلِیَآئِكَ وَمُعَادَاۃِ اَعْدَآئِكَ وَافْعَلْ بِیْ مَا اَنْتَ اَھْلُهٗ یَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSig